Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Shinigami-sama's pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:20.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you attend lessons from this afternoon on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick you up later, so get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Any response?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...even zombies can come out from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:39.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If a living person can't take a step out of that room, what are we to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She really hates me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:37.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I called out to her many times, but she's just so scared of coming out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:42.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, she told me she doesn't know how to deal with zombies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:48.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If all she does is sulk, then even I can't help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The quarters are just ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally be able to meet Crona!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:58.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good grasp on Crona's soul's wavelength, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:03.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get her used to Shibusen quickly, I'd like you to teach her whatever you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.74,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all, then I'll be glad to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:07.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting lost in such a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.38,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:17.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bad with directions! How much longer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.67,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She's finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.17,Copy of Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're at it, please show her around, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.80,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I've walked through here already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.64,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was gonna die from being lost back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you graduate from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.11,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A Delightful and Embarrassing Trial Attendance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibusen's New Lifestyle Assistance Fair In Session?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Devil Sword Wielder, Crona...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who inherited the madness that the witch Medusa left behind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:04:02.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By melting Ragnarok, a normal Demonic Weapon in the Black Blood, and infusing it into Crona,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a new form of Weapon and Meister were created.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:10.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To turn a Demonic Weapon into a Death Scythe, a witch's soul is required...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:18.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, the ones to make the Demonic Weapons evolve might not be the Meister, but the witches instead...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stand it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding back isn't good, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to tear things apart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything and everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know more about it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,About that child I made...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being infected with madness...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me for intruding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.41,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over {\i1}there{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The room's Mr. Smith calms me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give names to areas like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you around the school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue to get along, Crona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:36.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.52,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Marie-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:46.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you. I'm also starting out in this school, as a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, I'm just like you, Crona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.75,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Reassuring her by sharing the same worries...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice job, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Crona?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The blue person is looking over here! It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, stop doing that, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:12.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Sid-sensei looks like a blue hoodlum gorilla, he's really a nice person, so relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:17.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then! The short high-school life won't wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:23.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think everything will go your way, you annoying bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is. The little Ragnarok...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:32.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This was all your fault, you know?! Ugly woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't remember ever becoming one of your buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're like this, even if I get close, I won't be harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Those panties are even more boring than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:52.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Crona...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take a look, Crona...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... did I... {\alpha&HFF&}Did I say something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... did I... Did I say something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it? Being shown around the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you'll do okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, it's impossible for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, everyone's here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:19.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! I want to go back to the room's Mr. Smith...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you flying back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Write poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Write poetry, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:40.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when I feel down, I write lots of poetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious? You're a real gloomy one, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you some counseling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's write poetry together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If Maka says so...
