Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so dumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.16,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What... do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for being born...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How gloomy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:33.96,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With such a fine weather, what are you bean sprouts doing inside the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:39.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my existence is like that of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:43.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have worries, then behold me!\NI'm sure to brighten your paths!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:44.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for being born...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What great destructive power...
