Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for coming back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you were here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.47,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it concerns Crona.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:22.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some issues, but I believe she will get used to it some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But, somehow, you don't look so good, Sid-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, Crona is headed to the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:39.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,She's accompanying Maka on her extracurricular lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:46.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that most of the villagers are puppet engineers, so it's a pretty different village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:51.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the eldest golem that was built there suddenly started to act violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, there hasn't been any serious damage yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on... is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:07.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,These golems, you see, are there to protect something, and programmed only to defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:11.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting violently and destroying something is unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:15.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be related to the Wavelength of Madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:19.24,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid-kun, contact Stein-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear his opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the village of Loew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of chimneys, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a village that thrives on crafting golems, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably a kiln in every house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start gathering an abundance of souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing things like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're going to be students of Shibusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:56.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the rampaging golem we heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.48,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ask the villagers about the incident, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.32,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Puppet engineers... {\alpha&HFF&}Enchanters...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Puppet engineers... Enchanters...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:18.05,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This village's traditional huge gloves can amass magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they manipulate the earth and create golems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:25.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have welcoming faces at all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.97,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.23,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked about the golems, they all said they didn't know anything about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:36.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be hiding something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.07,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've been asking around about the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking for the rampaging golem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:51.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Giriko, an Enchanter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you around, so follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul, this is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what's so terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't really know yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.22,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:11.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}real{\i0} trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.77,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.06,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no clue either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul, I heard that Shinigami-sama knows what that terrible thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? As expected of Shinigami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He plays dumb, but he actually knows a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.15,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm gonna floor it! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:28.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we're in a hurry, but obey the speed limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, make sure you wear a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful you don't slip on wet floors too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in such a dark place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.58,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:22.17,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.14,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A message from Shinigami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The eldest golem in the village of Loew is on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a teapot, but what about the cups?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.03,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Pour it in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:50.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it seems like he wants to hear your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.83,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something peculiar about this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:15:00.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though a golem is created to ward off evil, it doesn't have a program to destroy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:05.88,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With the latest techniques, it's possible to craft a golem with a different program.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:10.13,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one that's causing the problem is the eldest golem...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be related to the Wavelength of Madness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.14,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's so, the sequence is weird, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The sequence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:24.31,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Kishin was revived, there hasn't been a single incident related to the Wavelength of Madness, fortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:30.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not unfathomable for a soulless golem going on a rampage is the first incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:35.28,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The first ones to be influenced should be humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:39.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, a golem being the first is certainly strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:45.04,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,A rampaging golem would, so to speak, mean a world that's already engulfed in a state of madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.63,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be odd if I'm still this frivolous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.68,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Shibusen's library.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Shinigami-sama that I would like some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But I went through the trouble of making coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, how much further until we reach the golem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.36,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been saying that for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,From this village, and from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This village, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...consists of people who sell golems to neighboring cities and countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.84,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance is protected by a ward against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's scared of things they don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.14,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that we're evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.51,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you immediately jump to that conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.02,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not trying to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.60,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:43.69,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:50.40,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to live quiet, peaceful lives in a village that people keep away from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So that we won't cause any conflict, we remained motionless like golems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,People are the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.87,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If they take off their mask of kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:05.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...the truth is, their hearts will be pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:07.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:15.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're an impatient woman, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like there's nothing more to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:33.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.70,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka, take stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:46.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Maka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? A golem is an object, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.21,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's not supposed to be alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can feel a soul's wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you're a young Meisterin, it seems like you've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.43,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...for as long as 800 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,With Enchanter techniques, I embedded my own memories into my own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:14.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeated this crappy, boring life around thirty times...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,800 years... what does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,This was all because of that Shinigami and his organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:25.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of opposing Shibusen, I needed to gather power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.67,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to say goodbye to being a "good boy..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a Meister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use {\i1}myself{\i0} with the golem {\i1}I{\i0} crafted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Demonic Weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.73,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, a golem with a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.86,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.95,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop making any more direct attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,As it is, if this goes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.33,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...your soul... {\alpha&HFF&}will be reaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...your soul... will be reaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't started the engine yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.46,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.01,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this wavelength?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.09,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an intense killing intent...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.18,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.89,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The engine's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:29.85,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul's wavelength...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...carries 800 years of killing intent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.98,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just from that one-hour of forcing myself to smile at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:39.57,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wouldn't be marked by Shibusen, I had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.78,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My life up to now was nothing! It was just crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoe! {\alpha&HFF&}Shot! Crack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.49,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoe! Shot! {\alpha&HFF&}Crack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:46.99,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoe! Shot! Crack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.37,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't have any meaning, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.25,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:08.93,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been, I can't remember how to enjoy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.81,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,My true self...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:14.27,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm... the words won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.82,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It's that... that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I kept building up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.61,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.53,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...want to destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.20,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was overwhelmed because of our difference in mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.62,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could attack from a range...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I show an opening, I'll be sent flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.79,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Crona's Screech Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.00,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.76,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're only supposed to observe, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.55,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.72,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you give me three pieces of candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnarok...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.39,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Four pieces, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.64,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a figure of speech! I don't really want any candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.56,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, I'm not a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.90,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,How about six pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.44,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter of how many!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:03.65,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.91,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,As many as you want! Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.12,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:14.29,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka Albarn, you have a way with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.71,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:21.42,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The rotation speed of the chainsaw didn't cut you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.59,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the Black Blood, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.10,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fought against that thing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:38.35,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad we became friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.19,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnarok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.45,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You've shrunk a little bit, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.66,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:54.50,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to hurt Maka any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:57.08,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're troubled and feel like writing poetry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:00.54,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,...then write with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:07.26,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Maka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:08.30,Soul basic,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
